Title: Brick and Ball Game

Description:
The Brick and Ball game is a simple Brick breaker game in which there is a ball that bounces of a platform to break a brick wall and the player has to keep the ball going by making sure the board is always there to bounce off the ball back.
The game will have three levels of difficulty, Beginner, Intermediate and  Advanced
Each level has different number of bricks and different speed of the ball

Enjoy our game!
